{"title":"直顶天上北斗星——仿客家山歌","authors":["萧殷"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":10,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"直顶天上北斗星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——仿客家山歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萧殷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村庄外面一片金，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谷穗绵绵连千顷；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵横小溪隔不断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山连山来金连金。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放眼四望望不尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渺渺茫茫比海深；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫说白鹭难飞过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老鹰飞起也担心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鹧鸪连声赞“谷好！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑的柳枝也弯身！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若把谷粒堆成山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谷堆定插天门顶；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫说顶破岭上云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直顶天上北斗星！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}